videos.description: Colten Rastetter mishandles the snap on the punt and gets tackled for a loss to set up Nebraska in the red zone.
videos.headline: Iowa's punter drops snap

videos.description: Nebraska's Stanley Morgan Jr. makes a great one-handed catch for the Cornhuskers touchdown.
videos.headline: Morgan hauls in nice TD grab

videos.description: Akrum Wadley uses a nice cut and sprints in for the 20-yard score.
videos.headline: Wadley eludes defender for Iowa TD

videos.description: Tanner Lee delivers a nice ball to Stanley Morgan Jr., who walks in for the easy score.
videos.headline: Lee hits Morgan for Nebraska TD

videos.description: Nathan Stanley rolls right and finds tight end Noah Fant for the tying touchdown.
videos.headline: Fant hauls in Iowa TD

videos.description: Akrum Wadley runs it in from one yard out to give the Hawkeyes the lead.
videos.headline: Wadley plunges in for Iowa TD

videos.description: Iowa's Nathan Stanley hooks up with Noah Fant for a 44-yard pass to set up a touchdown.
videos.headline: Stanley goes long to Fant

videos.description: James Butler bursts through the hole and scores from 12 yards out.
videos.headline: Butler dances his way in for Iowa TD

videos.description: Akrum Wadley goes untouched for a 29-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Iowa's Wadley scores again

videos.description: Iowa's Noah Fant takes the short pass and streaks down the sideline for the long Iowa touchdown.
videos.headline: Fant takes off for 68-yard score

videos.description: Toren Young runs in another short touchdown to extend the Iowa lead.
videos.headline: Young piles it on for Iowa

videos.description: Ivory Kelly-Martin is the fourth different Iowa running back to find the endzone as the Hawkeyes blow out Nebraska.
videos.headline: Kelly-Martin joins in on the fun

videos.description: Kristian Welch grabs the deflected pass for Iowa's third interception of the game.
videos.headline: Welch catches tipped pass for pick
